These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, mechanic
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, chinese
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, boat
1. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the architect is on the right of the mechanic##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | water      | iced-tea    |
| Job           | mechanic | architect |
| Nationality   | canadian       | chinese  |
| Transport     | roller      | boat     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: carrot, lime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, d&b
2 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, trike
1. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
2. the person eating lime is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | lime | carrot |
| Music-Genre   | house       | d&b         |
| Pet           | chinchilla     | fish         |
| Transport     | trike    | skateboard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, magic-tricks
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, paramedic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, gospel
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter
1. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the coach##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks          | video-games |
| Job           | paramedic | coach     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep            | gospel         |
| Transport     | helicopter         | motorbike   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
