The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, jazz
2 different pets are kept: pony, rabbit
1. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
2. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the pony##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | sprite     | water   |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary    | adventure |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | jazz |
| Pet           | pony | rabbit    |

