.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
There 2 different types of food: plum, avocado
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, van
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person eating plum is the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of ambient is the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | water     | hot-chocolate |
| Food          | avocado   | plum |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | ambient     |
| Transport     | boat | van     |

 